Requirements for running the app:
1- python tkinter
2- python customtkinter
3- python CTkListbox
4- python tkcalendar
5- python CTkMessagebox
6- python pathlib
7- python pickle
8- python bcrypt


how to run:
1- Comment app loop in controller file.
2- Uncomment add manager part to add a first user.
3- Comment add manager part.
4- Uncomment app loop.
5- use aaa for password and username for the first user to login as a manager.

